languages.text: {n}Группа подготовленных псайкеров обрушилась на Ноль-Халифа внезапно. Атакуя его могучий разум дарами варпа, они транслировали одну и ту же мысль: "Покорись!".{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}The Malateks bound the ancient machine spirit in the chains of data-vows and performed enigmatic rituals capable of subduing even the most wilful xenomachines. When the sacred calculations were complete, Null Caliph's tireless, unblinking eye began its watch over warp currents, protecting travellers from peril, and the Malateks' forbidden xenorituals filled the trove of the Rogue Trader's knowledge.{/n}

{n}The technomancers bound the ancient machine spirit in chains of data-vows and performed the enigmatic rituals they had received from Yrliet. Null Caliph's wisdom will fill the trove of Rogue Trader's knowledge, and so will the forbidden secrets of xeno magic.{/n}
